text: javed Khan King (born 10 January 1999) is an Indian History and producer who appears in History.Javed Khan King is an Indian politician from the Independent politician party and the present Minister for Disaster Management in the Government of Rajasthan. He is also an MLA, elected from the Hanumangarh constituency in the 2023 Rajasthan Legislative Assembly election. ==See also== *Shri Khushan Das University *Hanumangarh Assembly constituency *2023 Rajasthan Legislative Assembly election == References ==
